    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1004640/extras/3f1b43ed9d21ccdd841327d1edf6b45c.poster.avif?t=1766385464\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1004640/extras/3f1b43ed9d21ccdd841327d1edf6b45c.webm?t=1766385464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1004640/extras/3f1b43ed9d21ccdd841327d1edf6b45c.mp4?t=1766385464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1004640/extras/944b065d1f6186b8787b90577faf37c3.poster.avif?t=1766385464\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1004640/extras/944b065d1f6186b8787b90577faf37c3.webm?t=1766385464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1004640/extras/944b065d1f6186b8787b90577faf37c3.mp4?t=1766385464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>受太阳与圣印保佑，由双头狮统治的国家――――Ivalice。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ivalice与邻国Ordallia展开“The Fifty Years' War”却战败。一年后先王病逝，而将要继承王位的王子年仅两岁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此后为争夺监护人的头衔与实权，在“The Fifty Years' War”立下战功的两位将军：Duke Druksmald Goltanna和Duke Bestrald Larg的关系日渐紧张。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Duke Druksmald Goltanna以黑狮为家徽；Duke Bestrald Larg以白狮为家徽。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >二者的冲突日后被称为“The War of the Lions”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ramza是Ivalice知名武将House Beoulve的三儿子，而Delita则是普通平民，却与Ramza一起被扶养长大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这对童年玩伴的未来也同样被卷入混乱时代的旋涡中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■战斗系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1004640/extras/dc9fa1c34e723b17b749c3103cd221a3.poster.avif?t=1766385464\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1004640/extras/dc9fa1c34e723b17b749c3103cd221a3.webm?t=1766385464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1004640/extras/dc9fa1c34e723b17b749c3103cd221a3.mp4?t=1766385464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>本作战斗系统是紧张刺激的战斗模拟，角色走位和预判敌方行动会是胜利关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用具有高低差的3D地图，巧妙控制每个单位的行动顺序，获得胜利吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■组合与成长</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1004640/extras/7640b9e54e941843055c31df7e184a0d.poster.avif?t=1766385464\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1004640/extras/7640b9e54e941843055c31df7e184a0d.webm?t=1766385464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1004640/extras/7640b9e54e941843055c31df7e184a0d.mp4?t=1766385464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>通过诸多职业和技能的组合，实现丰富的战略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各角色成长后，就能转换为各种职业。每个职业都能学会各有特征的技能，而学会的技能即使转为其他职业也可使用。将职业与数百种技能组合搭配，打造只属于你的战术吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中有二十种以上富有特征的职业，其中也包括白魔道士、黑魔道士和龙骑士等为人所知的“FINAL FANTASY”系列职业。还有陆行鸟等怪物也可成为伙伴编组进队伍。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■两种模式：Enhanced Version与Classic Version</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1004640/extras/ca7627f66cb3c2c158a6fe9114550cbf.poster.avif?t=1766385464\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1004640/extras/ca7627f66cb3c2c158a6fe9114550cbf.webm?t=1766385464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1004640/extras/ca7627f66cb3c2c158a6fe9114550cbf.mp4?t=1766385464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>“Enhanced Version”追求沉浸感且更容易上手，“Classic Version”则重现原汁原味的回忆</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“Enhanced Version”中画面变得更加精美，并支持全语音，可以更深度沉浸于Ivalice的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同时为了方便游玩调整了部分系统与战斗，还追加了难度“Squire”，即使是第一次接触的玩家也不用担心，是任何人都能快乐游玩的模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当然也有尽可能忠实再现1997年发售的原版游玩体验的“Classic Version”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>“Enhanced Version”支持各类控制器。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>也可使用键盘与鼠标操作。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1004640/extras/b18d734e90a83460cf0fcaaaa7f164c6.avif?t=1766385464\" width=780 height=281 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>“Classic Version”的控制器仅支持XInput。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>虽然支持键盘操作，但不支持鼠标操作。</i></p>",
